you complete me

https://github.com/Valloric/YouCompleteMe

vim package for autocompletion.  Needs to be compiled before it is used. Needs an extra flags file per project for the GoTo commands to work - haven't gotten this all set up yet.

There is a generator that is supposed to make the ycm_extra_conf file automatically?
